Data Deletion Instructions
Your Right to Data Deletion
In accordance with applicable data protection laws, you have the right to request the deletion of your personal data that we hold. Below are the steps you can take to request data deletion:

How to Request Data Deletion
1)Email Request: 
  Send an email to our Data Protection Officer at info@cloudcrapsolutions.com. The email should include:
  Your full name
  The email address associated with your account
  A clear statement that you are requesting the deletion of your personal data
2) Through the App: 
  If our app has a user settings page, navigate to the 'Privacy Settings' section and click on the 'Request Data Deletion' button. Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the request.

3) Customer Support: 
  Contact our customer support team via [Support Channel, e.g., live chat, phone] and request data deletion. You may be asked to verify your identity before the request is processed.

Verification Process
To protect your information, we may require you to verify your identity before proceeding with the data deletion request. This may include asking you to provide additional information or documents.

Timeframe
Upon receiving a verified request, we will process it within 24 hours as required by applicable laws.

Exceptions
There may be circumstances where we cannot delete all of your personal data due to legal obligations or other reasons. In such cases, we will inform you of the reason and the specific data that cannot be deleted.

